{"tid":760932,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴稱曼聯需要拿下獎盃 否則就是失敗","createTime":"2018-07-30T03:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T09:11:33.000Z","uid":161311,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9fec46e9f0e6fac97096fb5b4120679778213a","tid":760932,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"現年36歲的前曼聯球員伊巴謙莫域在周五表示，曼聯要在這個球季拿下獎盃來證明自己，要不然，這就是一個失敗的球季。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴說：「摩連奴是一個為冠而生的人，但去年曼聯並沒有贏過任何獎盃，以他花的資源，是不太合理的。曼聯是一家大會，不能只以表現來衡量功過，獎盃也很重要。」這名瑞典前鋒在2016年曾經效力曼聯，在曼聯踢了一年半，在首季為曼聯為下汗馬功勞，在向項賽事48場射入28球，助紅魔鬼拿下了英聯盃和歐霸盃兩個盃賽冠軍。但在去季，曼聯在花掉大筆轉會資金買下盧卡古、阿歷斯山齊士、尼曼查馬迪等人，連計前季的保羅普巴等，四大皆空絕對是不能收貨。<br />\n<br />\n這名現效力洛杉磯銀河的前鋒亦向舊東家送上祝福：「摩連奴已經準備好他的球隊，我認為他們會有一個好球季，曼聯這兩年有不少好的新球員，他們已建立一個很好的體系，我也祝福他們能在新球季中獲得成功，因為他們絕對有成功的實力。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180728/58494146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58494146&d=2NJl0nWDkMNMwnfaPeqvKDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f6a6229f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58494146&h=560226f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180728/58494146</a>"},{"pid":"9e8a8bd5cbe63934f5b9f3fcd50b5b173a37763f","tid":760932,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人系列"},{"pid":"21d5c6b007fff79c918ab89a84910d31bc49d08b","tid":760932,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7691e0c30230e72d9914a8b32ecf3e0a96d4b097","tid":760932,"uid":44890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/114757_ca42a3e2dc3c108335c60320b3ab0625.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F114757_ca42a3e2dc3c108335c60320b3ab0625.png&h=d93326bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做咩撚野客入到咁多球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509a0859eb334fed7226b9cc5d062cf733f384d9","tid":760932,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"9de939c96e1ada8dbc4af43265c43c981f05014b","tid":760932,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"乜盃先得架?足總盃又係盃"},{"pid":"012b75ec09a4da4709f89e3fc96f765a1db48613","tid":760932,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"踢到嘔白泡先險勝修記捧雞盃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}